Int.name: jale
Int.description:
Jale was an alternative rock band from Halifax, Nova Scotia, on the east coast of 
Canada. Contemporaries of Sloan and The Super Friendz, they were formed in 
1992 and disbanded in 1996. They released three records in all (the albums 
Dreamcake and So Wound and the EP "Closed").
